    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奥林匹斯骰子》（Dice of Olympus）是一款策略游戏，使用可定制的骰子作为游戏机制，在战役模式中击败在线玩家或怪物。游戏让玩家沉浸在希腊神话及其伟大史诗的世界中。您可以扮演奥林匹斯众神，在多人模式中与来自 “地狱之渊 ”监狱的怪物或其他玩家进行战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/7ed4d6030d6cb213b5d0e717a60e88fb.avif?t=1751445750\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><br>神庙是您定制骰子牌组的地方。慢慢阅读您所掌握的众多牌面的说明，并将它们明智地分配到您的骰子中，以创造协同效应和真正的绝妙组合。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/bf606a9f015e2024d3a1f3a3fabcfdbb.poster.avif?t=1751445750\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/bf606a9f015e2024d3a1f3a3fabcfdbb.webm?t=1751445750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/bf606a9f015e2024d3a1f3a3fabcfdbb.mp4?t=1751445750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/41c1c4965856196791709fbd353ee60c.avif?t=1751445750\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br>选择拥有独特法术的神灵，用 5 颗骰子的多种面值（约 100 种）定制自己的骰子，利用所有游戏机制来构建一个无懈可击的战略。在你的卡组中放入所有你需要的法术，以挫败对手的战略，使你摆脱最糟糕的局面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦进入战斗，尽一切可能获得最好的抽牌结果，不要太贪心，明智地选择掷骰子、发射法术及其目标。一个回合一个回合地制定计划，预测最好和最坏的情况，将对手的生命值降到零。在《奥林匹斯骰子》中，您可以..：<br><br>攻击健康点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阻挡对手的骰子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >增加掷骰子的次数，确保获得你想要的东西</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >增加你的好感度以获得独特的奖励</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召唤魔法水晶，获得奖励或诅咒</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得法力值以发动更大的法术</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有更多其他法术机制等着您去发现...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/8c6ca727e615f74c3181f3ef2bf13509.avif?t=1751445750\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br>当您进入战斗时，游戏将从您自定义的 5 个骰子中只为您提供 3 个，在这 3 个骰子中，如果您不想以此开始游戏，您只能更改其中一个，一旦 “闷棍 ”阶段结束，真正的战斗就可以开始了！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/cdd68ba7de8f7204c35e05fcf36044e2.poster.avif?t=1751445750\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/cdd68ba7de8f7204c35e05fcf36044e2.webm?t=1751445750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/cdd68ba7de8f7204c35e05fcf36044e2.mp4?t=1751445750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/13a4882d4f0bceb0384b6f9adf9d4aad.avif?t=1751445750\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br>当您进入战斗时，游戏将从您自定义的 5 个骰子中只为您提供 3 个，在这 3 个骰子中，如果您不想以此开始游戏，您只能更改其中一个，一旦 “闷棍 ”阶段结束，真正的战斗就可以开始了！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/11c0c2e344f4bdc3ed27ea23c1ed0b18.poster.avif?t=1751445750\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/11c0c2e344f4bdc3ed27ea23c1ed0b18.webm?t=1751445750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/11c0c2e344f4bdc3ed27ea23c1ed0b18.mp4?t=1751445750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/7b09ea30fc7334cdb4fa3765a82e9bee.avif?t=1751445750\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><br>一旦准备就绪，您就可以向对手施放法术了。为了决定哪位玩家可以施放法术，哪位玩家需要等待，我们创建了一个咒语分数，每个法术都有一个法力值和一个咒语值，当您的咒语分数小于对手时，您就可以施放法术，直到您的咒语分数超过对手的咒语分数为止。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/5a43c132982abcc3a0b40c6c4302c4cd.poster.avif?t=1751445750\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/5a43c132982abcc3a0b40c6c4302c4cd.webm?t=1751445750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/5a43c132982abcc3a0b40c6c4302c4cd.mp4?t=1751445750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每 3 个回合，您可以选择解锁一个额外的骰子或在游戏剩余时间获得一个法力点，因此请明智地选择哪种奖励会让您在游戏中脱颖而出。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/099e8398ce771a1a0c407ecd37db2198.poster.avif?t=1751445750\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/099e8398ce771a1a0c407ecd37db2198.webm?t=1751445750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/099e8398ce771a1a0c407ecd37db2198.mp4?t=1751445750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/ee350838013c743ae6ed51b340aa98b6.avif?t=1751445750\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br>游戏以掷骰子为基础，因此具有随机性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，不受控制的随机性会让玩家产生强烈的挫败感、不公平感和无助感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了解决这个问题，我们决定，当您掷骰子时，保证您掷出的骰子会与前一个骰子不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有了这一小小的变化，您就可以在铣削游戏的基础上创建策略，例如<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515580/extras/a39b4739c1455e6c64b08685852d314f.avif?t=1751445750\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><br>在《奥林匹斯骰子》中，您可以进行两种游戏模式。冒险模式将建议您与从 “地狱之渊 ”监狱逃出的怪物作战。1 对 1 的多人模式，可与您的朋友或世界各地的玩家对战。</p>",
